The paper proposes a new search heuristic based on the concept of evolvability, which is a common topic in the field of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of fitness landscapes, which is a common topic in the field of data structures (cs.DS) and optimization (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper applies the proposed heuristic to a travelling salesman problem, which is a classic problem in the field of computational complexity (cs.CE).
